                        <title>Barlaams saga ok Jósaphats</title>; <origPlace>Iceland</origPlace>, <origDate notBefore="1350" notAfter="1399" cert="high" evidence="conjecture">s. XIV<hi rend="sup">2</hi></origDate>. </head>
                    <msContents>
